# Build outputs & dependencies (restored/installed inside the image)
**/bin
**/obj
**/node_modules
**/wwwroot

# Local secrets & dev artifacts — never ship these into the image
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/appsettings.Development.json
**/Logs
**/DevelopmentEmails
**/Emails

# VCS / IDE / misc
.git
.gitignore
.github
.vs
.vscode
.idea
**/*.user
Dockerfile
.dockerignore
README.md
.claude
scratch-*.html
